{
  "stem": "7832.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just had no choice anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But by April, we were somewhere in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the Pilsen area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we knew that we were close to Czechoslovakia-- that used to be Czechoslovakia anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were-- we were just marching and marching.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "One night they-- they gave us-- we passed a town and there were a lot of farms in that town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The snow-- this was still like in January, February.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they-- they led us into a farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By then we were only about maybe 2,000 people because the rest they killed on the side of the road that couldn't keep up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they led us in-- onto this farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they let us in through the farm-- like the stalls where they used to have the-- it was-- it was empty.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They just had a lot of hay in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so they had like two stories of this-- this-- this-- this-- this building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so they let us spend the night there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Like the farmer told them that we could spent the night there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so they led us in there into that building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they locked us in there, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And inside at least there was hay so we were warm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And up on the second floor, the farmer, they stored fruits and vegetables for the winter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So it was all packed in and covered with hay so it doesn't freeze.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, one of the inmates managed to get up there and found the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because, see, everybody was always scavenging for what they-- what they can-- what we can eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they found all this food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But he-- he-- she-- she came down with all this food and closed up the entrance where-- where she went up.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
